 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the indonesian##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the german is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the german and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Nationality       | german        | pakistani   | chinese  | indonesian   | thai |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

